    "description_long": "This is a small, enclosed graveyard scene surrounded by a wooden picket fence. Inside, there are six gray tombstones, each inscribed with 'R.I.P.', arranged in two rows. Several orange pumpkins are scattered throughout the graveyard, adding a seasonal or Halloween touch. A single, leafless, gnarled tree stands in one corner, its twisted branches reaching upward. Near the center, a small ghost figure with a white sheet and black eyes hovers above the ground. The ground surface is flat and appears to be a muted, earthy color, simulating soil or grass.",
